thany, Oklahoma|Bethany]] || [[Oklahoma]] || [[Sooner Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Southwestern College (Kansas)|Southwestern College]]\n| [[Southwestern Moundbuilders|Moundbuilders]] || [[Winfield, Kansas|Winfield]] || [[Kansas]] || [[Kansas Collegiate Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Spring Arbor University]]\n| Cougars || [[Spring Arbor, Michigan|Spring Arbor]] || [[Michigan]] || [[Crossroads League]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Stephens College]]\n| Stars || [[Columbia, Missouri|Columbia]] || [[Missouri]] || [[American Midwest Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Sterling College (Kansas)|Sterling College]]\n| [[Sterling Warriors|Warriors]] || [[Sterling, Kansas|Sterling]] || [[Kansas]] || [[Kansas Collegiate Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Stillman College]]\n| Tigers || [[Tuscaloosa, Alabama|Tuscaloosa]] || [[Alabama]] || [[Southern States Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Tabor College (Kansas)|Tabor College]]\n| [[Tabor Bluejays|Bluejays]] || [[Hillsboro, Kansas|Hillsboro]] || [[Kansas]] || [[Kansas Collegiate Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Talladega College]]\n| Tornadoes || [[Talladega, Alabama|Talladega]] || [[Alabama]] || [[Gulf Coast Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Taylor University]]\n| Trojans || [[Upland, Indiana|Upland]] || [[Indiana]] || [[Crossroads League]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Tennessee Wesleyan College]]\n| Bulldogs || [[Athens, Tennessee|Athens]] || [[Tennessee]] || [[Appalachian Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Texas A&M University\u2013Texarkana]]*\n| Eagles || [[Texarkana, Texas|Texarkana]] || [[Texas]] || [[Red River Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Texas College]]\n| Steers || [[Tyler, Texas|Tyler]] || [[Texas]] || [[Red River Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Texas Wesleyan University]]\n| Rams || [[Fort Worth, Texas|Fort Worth]] || [[Texas]] || [[Sooner Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Thomas University]]\n| [[Thomas University Night Hawks|Night Hawks]] || [[Thomasvil