ly Springs, Mississippi|Holly Springs]] || [[Mississippi]] || [[Gulf Coast Athletic Conference]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gcaconf.com/members.php#250|title=Gulf Coast Athletic Conference - Members|website=www.gcaconf.com|accessdate=September 7, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Saint Ambrose|[[St. Ambrose University]]}}\n| Fighting Bees & Queen Bees || [[Davenport, Iowa|Davenport]] || [[Iowa]] || [[Chicagoland Collegiate Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Saint Andrews|[[St. Andrews University (North Carolina)|St. Andrews University]]}}\n| [[St. Andrews University Knights|Knights]] || [[Laurinburg, North Carolina|Laurinburg]] || [[North Carolina]] || [[Appalachian Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Saint Francis (IL)|[[University of St. Francis]]}}\n| Fighting Saints || [[Joliet, Illinois|Joliet]] || [[Illinois]] || [[Chicagoland Collegiate Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Saint Francis (IN)|[[University of Saint Francis (Indiana)|University of Saint Francis]]}}\n| Cougars || [[Fort Wayne, Indiana|Fort Wayne]] || [[Indiana]] || [[Crossroads League]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Saint Katherine|[[University of Saint Katherine]]}}\n| Firebirds || [[San Marcos, California|San Marcos]] || [[California]] || [[California Pacific Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Saint Louis Pharmacy|[[St. Louis College of Pharmacy]]}}\n| Eutectics || {{sort|Saint Louis|[[St. Louis]]}} || [[Missouri]] || [[American Midwest Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Saint Mary|[[University of Saint Mary]]}}\n| [[Saint Mary Spires|Spires]] || [[Leavenworth, Kansas|Leavenworth]] || [[Kansas]] || [[Kansas Collegiate Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Saint Mary College|[[College of Saint Mary]]}}\n| Flames || [[Omaha, Nebraska|Omaha]] || [[Nebraska]] || [[Great Plains Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Saint Thomas (FL)|[[St. Thomas University (Florida)|St. Thomas University]]}}\n| [[St. Thomas University Bobcats|Bobcats]] || [[Miami Gar